call.sql: SELECT DISTINCT t0.HEADER_ID, t0.ORDER_NUMBER, t0.VERSION_NUMBER, t0.ORDER_SOURCE_ID, t0.ORIG_SYS_DOCUMENT_REF, t0.ORDERED_DATE, t0.TRANSACTIONAL_CURR_CODE, t0.CUST_PO_NUMBER, t0.SHIPPING_METHOD_CODE, t0.CREATION_DATE, t0.CREATED_BY, t0.LAST_UPDATED_BY, t0.LAST_UPDATE_DATE, t0.CANCELLED_FLAG, t0.OPEN_FLAG, t0.BOOKED_FLAG, t0.ORDER_CATEGORY_CODE, t0.FLOW_STATUS_CODE, t0.SALESREP_ID, t0.SHIP_TO_ORG_ID, t0.INVOICE_TO_ORG_ID, t0.SOLD_TO_ORG_ID, t0.ORG_ID, t0.ORDER_TYPE_ID FROM HR_OPERATING_UNITS t4, HZ_CUST_ACCOUNTS t3, HZ_PARTIES t2, OE_ORDER_LINES_ALL t1, OE_ORDER_HEADERS_ALL t0 WHERE t0.ORDER_NUMBER = NVL(#pOrderNumber,t0.ORDER_NUMBER) AND t0.ORIG_SYS_DOCUMENT_REF = NVL(#pOrigSysDocumentRef,t0.ORIG_SYS_DOCUMENT_REF) AND t0.ORG_ID = NVL(#pOrganizationId,t0.ORG_ID) AND t1.HEADER_ID = t0.HEADER_ID AND t3.CUST_ACCOUNT_ID = t0.SOLD_TO_ORG_ID AND t2.PARTY_ID = t3.PARTY_ID AND t4.ORGANIZATION_ID=t0.ORG_ID and t4.SHORT_CODE=NVL(#pOrganizationCode,t4.SHORT_CODE) AND t1.LINE_NUMBER = NVL(#pLineNumber,t1.LINE_NUMBER) AND t1.SHIPMENT_NUMBER = NVL(#pShipmentNumber,t1.SHIPMENT_NUMBER) AND t2.PARTY_NAME = NVL(#pSoldToCustomerName,t2.PARTY_NAME) AND t0.FLOW_STATUS_CODE = NVL(#pFlowStatusCode, t0.FLOW_STATUS_CODE) AND t3.ACCOUNT_NUMBER = NVL(#pSoldToCustomerNumber,t3.ACCOUNT_NUMBER) AND t0.HEADER_ID = NVL(#pHeaderId,t0.HEADER_ID) ORDER BY t0.LAST_UPDATE_DATE DESC FETCH FIRST #pNumRows ROWS ONLY
